      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_51",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "“gaji  yang  akhir  diterima”  ertinya  gaji  hakiki  bulanan  yang  akhir",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_52",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "diterima dan termasuklah apa-apa elaun berpencen;",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_53",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "“Ketua Pengarah” ertinya Ketua Pengarah Perkhidmatan Awam;",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_54",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "“Ordinan”  ertinya  Ordinan  Pencen  1951[Ord.1  tahun  1951], \nOrdinan  Pencen  Sabah  1963  [Ord.  3  tahun  1963],  Ordinan  Pencen \nSarawak [Bab 89] dan segala Peraturan yang dibuat di bawahnya;",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_55",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "“pegawai”  ertinya  semua  kategori  pegawai  sebagaimana  yang",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_56",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "ditakrifkan dalam Ordinan itu;",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_57",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "“pegawai berpencen” ertinya pegawai  yang telah diletakkan dalam",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_58",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "perjawatan berpencen berdasarkan Skim di bawah Ordinan itu;",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_59",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "“perkhidmatan",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_60",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "ertinya \nboleh \nperkhidmatan yang boleh dimasukira di bawah Ordinan itu;",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_61",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "dimasukira”",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_62",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "yang",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_63",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "tempoh",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_64",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "“Skim” ertinya gaji dan terma serta syarat perkhidmatan yang telah \ndipinda  bagi  pegawai  dalam  perkhidmatan  awam  berdasarkan  syor \noleh  Suruhanjaya  Diraja  Suffian  dan  Suruhanjaya    Diraja  Aziz \nmengenai  gaji  dan  terma  serta  syarat  perkhidmatan  bagi  pegawai \nsedemikian itu yang dibuat oleh Kerajaan Persekutuan.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_65",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Penghitungan Semula Pencen",
